text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It combines information on suffrage, the freedom
and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and expression, as well as the extent to which citizens can engage in regional and local
government, civil society organizations and direct democracy. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
